# Ticket #3 – Disabled User Account

## Issue:
The user is attempting to login to their account but their account is disabled

## Investigation:
Opened Active Directory and the client computer
Located the user account
Verified that the account is disabled

## Root Cause:
The user is a rehired employee attempting to login to a disabled user account

## Resolution:
Logged in to Active Directory
Enabled the user account
Set a temporary password for the user
Verified that the user logged in using the temporary password

## Verification:
User changed their password and logged into their account successfully
